         ...
         controller {
           socket_directory = &quot;/var/run/myapp_sockets&quot;;
           max_level = &quot;debug&quot;;
           logging { ... };
         }
         ...
       }</precode><newline/>The <code>socket_directory</code> overrides the location where the special
directory with Unix Domain sockets and other runtime files is
created.<newline/>The <code>max_level</code> parameter defines the global maximum log level.
It defaults to &quot;info&quot;. By setting it to &quot;debug&quot; (as shown) debug
